title: Ep. 323 - The Cynical Attack On Joe Biden
description:
Joe Biden is facing intense scrutiny for behavior he’s been exhibited in public, including on the largest stage in the world, for 40 years. We will analyze Joe Biden’s #MeToo moment. Then, AOC hits primetime on left-wing cable news, and a NYT columnist dumps his girlfriend because she’s white. Date: 04-01-2019
